---
title: Teriyaki Chicken & Roast Pumpkin Salad with Pickled Onion & Peanuts
description: Enjoy this sweet and savoury glazed chicken with umami-rich teriyaki sauce for an easy meal that doesn't skimp on flavour! With colourful roasted veggies and crunchy peanuts, it's a family-friendly meal that will have everyone satisfied.
